overview.en: The Aibocoin foundation is an operation team serving the global chess game market technology development. With rich experience in game algorithm technology, with a large number of industry technical experts and authoritative technical consultants, it provides the underlying technology engine and scientific algorithm for more than many game platforms worldwide.
overview.zh: Aibocoin基金会是一家服务于全球棋牌游戏市场技术开发的运营团队。 具有丰富经验游戏算法的技术，拥有大量的行业技术专家和权威技术顾问，为 全球超过诸多游戏平台提供底层技术引擎和科学算法。
